INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (13,5,'2017-01-11 20:29:39','2017-01-11 20:29:39','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Welcome to my WordPress adventure! Can you feel the stoke?!! I\'m officially switching over from the tired old html website to this snazzy new WP site.  I\'ll try to keep up with my blog in the near future. For now I\'ll take all the criticisms and compliments you will throw at me.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">But seriously, speaking of compliments..</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/upIgwkDSvpAWY/giphy.gif\" width=\"575\" height=\"404\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Haha! I just couldn\'t resist.. :D</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Cheers!</p>','Woo Hoo! It\'s Wordpress!','','publish','open','open','','woo-hoo-its-wordpress','','','2017-03-03 10:21:48','2017-03-03 18:21:48','',0,'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/?p=13',0,'post','',0),(15,5,'2017-01-11 20:32:33','2017-01-11 20:32:33','<div class=\"front-work\">\r\n<h1>Natalie Rose ~ Front-End &amp; WordPress Developer</h1>\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<h2>I build websites for blogs and small businesses.\r\nI am experienced in responsive design and specialize in developing custom WordPress themes. WordPress Developer.</h2>\r\nWordPress Developer. Websites are essential for small businesses these days. Especially on mobile responsive sites.\r\nIf you are an individual with services, products, or inspiration to share, there is no better way to reach people around the world than with your own website or blog.\r\n\r\nBecause WordPress development can be tricky if you don\'t know a lot of code.\r\nIf you are struggling with WordPress themes and customizations, or you want a custom website tailored specifically to you, I\'m here to help!\r\nBecause running a business or blog takes a lot of time and dedication.\r\n\r\n<strong>You work hard. You\'re busy. I get that!</strong>\r\n\r\nLet me build or customize your website so you can get back to the work you love!\r\n<div id=\"work-more\">\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://natalierose.wpengine.com/wordpress/portfolio/\">Learn more..</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"front-about\">\r\n<div id=\"front-about-img\"><img class=\"alignnone\" title=\"Natalie Rose, Front-End &amp; WordPress Developer\" src=\"https://natalierose.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/natalierose-about-img2.png\" alt=\"Natalie Rose, Front-End &amp; WordPress Developer\" width=\"294\" height=\"293\" /></div>\r\n<div id=\"front-about-text\">\r\n<h3>I craft dynamic custom websites so you can turn your dreams into a profitable reality. WordPress Developer.</h3>\r\nI\'m a busy 30-something millenial, currently living on beautiful Vancouver Island, Canada. I love to create powerful, easy to use, and fully responsive websites that stand out among the crowd. I build websites from scratch and have experience editing and updating existing websites and dynamic web applications. WordPress Developer.\r\n<div id=\"about-more\">\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://natalierose.wpengine.com/wordpress/about/\">Learn more about me..</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nI design in the browser with HTML5, CSS3 and a touch of JavaScript. I love coding things from scratch and can work with existing front-end frameworks as well. Therefore I can do almost anything you want!\r\n\r\nWordPress is the content management system I specialize in and prefer for my clients. WordPress powers the site’s back-end interface and makes website management easy. I excel in customizing WordPress child themes for a unique design and creating custom themes from scratch.\r\n\r\nResponsive WordPress development will make your website easily accessible across all devices. As the number of people using mobile devices to access the internet grows, make sure that your website offers all users a great experience.\r\n<h4>WordPress Developer. Front-End Developer.</h4>\r\n<a href=\"http://natalierose.wpengine.com/about/\">About Me</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://natalierose.wpengine.com/portfolio/\">Work</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://natalierose.wpengine.com/blog/\">Blog</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.upwork.com/hire/wordpress-developers/\">Outbound</a>\r\n\r\n2<a href=\"https://www.billerickson.net/\">Outbound</a>\r\n\r\n3<a href=\"https://www.freelancer.com/find/Wordpress?gclid=CKq0k_Ho7dMCFW4A0wode94D0g\">Outbound</a>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">I specialize in custom wordpress themes and responsive development! I can add almost any feature you desire to your HTML or WordPress website. I\'ll optimize your images to help speed up your load time and transform your static site into a fully responsive one that works beautifully across all devices.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">This is my passion and my own path to freedom. It’s what I love to do. I decided to embrace my own dreams of working for myself back in 2016. I\'ve since completed a year of schooling and am now a front-end and WordPress developer. I have many plans for the future. Including learning web and UI/UX design.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">I love supporting small businesses and the blogging community and strongly believe in co-operation and self-sustainability. I’d love to see more people break free from the current 9-5 work structure and I am thrilled when I can help people do just that!</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">In conclusion, hire a WordPress Developer like me!</p>','Natalie Rose Front-End & WordPress Developer - Home','','publish','closed','closed','','natalie-rose-front-end-wordpress-developer-home','','','2017-05-13 14:37:45','2017-05-13 21:37:45','',0,'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/?page_id=15',0,'page','',0),(20,5,'2017-01-11 18:06:34','2017-01-12 02:06:34','','Blog','','trash','closed','closed','','blog__trashed','','','2017-05-02 17:02:29','2017-05-03 00:02:29','',0,'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/?page_id=20',0,'page','',0),(47330,5,'2017-01-16 14:15:27','2017-01-16 22:15:27','<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-47582 alignright\" src=\"http://natalierose.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/nat6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Hello, and welcome to Natalie Rose.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">I\'m Natalie, a front-end and WordPress developer, artist and outdoor enthusiast. I\'m a busy 30-something millennial currently living on the beautiful west coast of Canada. I have many passions and hobbies and work hard so I can play even harder! I\'m in love with this amazing planet and strive to spend as much time as possible exploring the wild nooks and spectacular vistas nature has to offer. I love hiking and camping and I\'m working towards challenging myself on some longer through hiking adventures.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Naturally, I have a great interest in ecology, biology and conservation and strive to live as environmentally consciously as possible. I have a burning passion to protect the wild places and to help humanity live more in cinque with nature. There are so many incredible inventions, technologies, and new ideas discovered every day that I have great hope for the future! I believe the challenges we face these days are great, but with love and co-operation we can not only overcome these obstacles but evolve and thrive! My mission is to spread awareness, innovation, solutions and lots of love!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">I\'m also a creative soul and love to work with my hands and heart. I enjoy things like painting and woodworking, and the old-school homey arts such as gardening, farming, foraging, canning, and creating my own health and beauty products out of plant materials and essential oils.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Another passion of mine is to help people reach their professional dreams. As a front-end and WordPress developer I love to create beautiful, easy to use and fully functional websites. I work with amazing people; from bloggers to business owners and thoroughly enjoy digging into the deep caverns of code to help make websites that stand out among the crowd. I can build websites from scratch and have experience editing and updating existing websites and dynamic web applications. I\'m proficient in HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, JQuery, Git, Github, WordPress and Responsive design.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Does your website lose ease and functionality when accessed on mobile or tablet? There are so many websites out there that are so poorly designed and frustrating to use on a mobile, don\'t be one of them and lose out on customers or clients because of a bad mobile design. I can update an existing static website to a responsive design that works well across all browsers and platforms. Are you tired of html and want to switch over to the wonderful world of WordPress? I can make the switch over for you or help you with the process. Do you want something fresh, dynamic and unique? I can modify WordPress themes to make your website truly one of a kind and exactly the way you want.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Drop me a line and I\'ll see what I can do for you!</p>\r\n\r\n<h6 style=\"text-align: left;\">[wpforms id=\"47560\"]</h6>','About Me','','trash','closed','closed','','about-me__trashed','','','2017-05-02 17:01:50','2017-05-03 00:01:50','',0,'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/?page_id=47330',0,'page','',0),(47336,5,'2017-02-02 05:13:29','2017-02-02 05:13:29','','Facebook','','publish','closed','closed','','facebook','','','2017-03-03 09:46:31','2017-03-03 17:46:31','',0,'http://natalierose.wpengine.com/?p=47336',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(47338,5,'2017-02-02 05:13:30','2017-02-02 05:13:30','','Github','','publish','closed','closed','','github','','','2017-03-03 09:46:31','2017-03-03 17:46:31','',0,'http://natalierose.wpengine.com/?p=47338',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(47446,5,'2017-01-26 16:28:36','2017-01-27 00:28:36','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Finally! The day I have been waiting for is almost at hand! It\'s time to take this baby and shove her out into the cold vastness of the interwebs. Soon I shall have actual content and interesting things to share with my non-existent viewers.. but for now it\'s time to celebrate!!  Three cheers for the launch! Hip Hip Hooray!</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/1PMVNNKVIL8Ig/giphy.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Time to celebrate!</p>','She\'s going live!','','publish','open','open','','shes-going-live','','','2017-03-03 10:20:22','2017-03-03 18:20:22','',0,'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/?p=47446',0,'post','',0),(47501,5,'2017-02-01 12:26:26','2017-02-01 20:26:26','<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Thank You!</strong></h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Your comments and questions are appreciated!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">I will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-47568\" src=\"http://natalierose.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/cat1-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"645\" height=\"450\" /></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Thank You!','','publish','closed','closed','','thank-you','','','2017-03-05 22:45:11','2017-03-06 06:45:11','',0,'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/?page_id=47501',0,'page','',0),(47535,5,'2017-02-01 14:37:18','2017-02-01 22:37:18','<p>This is the WPForms preview page. All your form previews will be handled on this page.</p><p>The page is set to private, so it is not publically accessible. Please do not delete this page :) .</p>','WPForms Preview','','trash','closed','closed','','wpforms-preview__trashed','','','2017-05-03 11:19:50','2017-05-03 18:19:50','',0,'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/wpforms-preview/',0,'page','',0),(47540,5,'2017-02-02 05:58:24','2017-02-02 05:58:24','','Twitter','','publish','closed','closed','','twitter-2',''